metadata.name: Kraken The Icy Abyss #1
metadata.description: This is for adventurous souls who dare to journey into uncharted waters, across the dark icy abyss into the realm of the ice-shackled creature. The Kraken are creating history, and you can be a part of it. This one-of-a-kind tribute to their inaugural season is memorialized in never seen 3-D graphics of the Kraken lore.
